Oinker/Zergling


Oiinker walked into the brig. He looked around. Nobody was there. He 
sent a message to Zergling, "Excuse me Zerglin', but they is not in 
th' brig." 
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Zergling hear the message. "Idiot they moved to room 213." Zergling 
then checked the longrange sensors again. "Maximals please leave our 
longrange semsor range or Tavatron is dead. Zergling wants to kill."
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Oinker heard Zergling message about them changed room, "acco'din' t' 
th' code o' th' heells! Ohh okay, ah's on mah way." Oinker headed for 
the room with The 4 maximals in it.
